Assuming this photo is from after 1893, this is Margaret James Murray Washington.&quot;Margaret Murray Washington was the third wife of Booker T. Washington and Lady Principal of Tuskegee Normal and Industrial Institute, now Tuskegee University. She was born on March 9, 1865, in Macon, Mississippi and died on June 26, 1925 in Tuskegee Institute, Alabama. She was inducted into the Alabama Women's Hall of Fame in 1972.&quot;
